[2] UK (England)
Date: Mon 30 May 2022 7:31 PM GMT+2
Source: Reuters [edited]
https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/britain-says-71-more-monkeypox-cases-identified-england-2022-05-30/


There have been 71 additional cases of monkeypox identified in England, the UK Health Security Agency said on Monday [30 May 2022], taking the total number of confirmed cases in the United Kingdom as a whole since 7 May [2022] to 179.

[Byline: Alistair Smout; editing: David Goodman]

